// Portal Adapters Configuration
// Pre-configured adapters for major insurance credentialing portals

/**
 * Adapter Tiers:
 * - Tier 0: Unknown portal - uses generic engine only
 * - Tier 1: Config-only - JSON mapping of selectors and labels
 * - Tier 2: Config + navigation - handles multi-step flows
 * - Tier 3: Heavy customization - complex portals with custom code
 */

